-- IMF’s Lagarde Sees Scope for ECB Monetary Easing, FAZ Reports
-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 2012-04-18T06:51:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-18/imf-s-lagarde-sees-scope-for-ecb-monetary-easing-faz-reports.html
International Monetary Fund
Managing Director  Christine Lagarde  said the European Central
Bank has scope to help economic growth in the euro area where
low inflation prevails, the Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung
reported.  “We see good reasons for a monetary easing in those
industrial states in which inflation is under control -- there
is scope,” Lagarde is cited as saying in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Parkin in Berlin at 
